<html>

<head>
    <title></title>
    <link href="style.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <h1 class="pillowmaker">pillowmaker</h1>

    <div class="guestbook">
        <p>there are others resting in the place, please keep quiet and respect the space </p>
